427
00:37:04.930 --> 00:37:06.560
And I can't just let her crush me.

428
00:37:08.330 --> 00:37:10.130
I can't go back to the prosecution. either.

429
00:37:13.500 --> 00:37:14.500
Don't you...

430
00:37:15.610 --> 00:37:17.110
